{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"BroadcastChannel.postMessage()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/postMessage","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/name\"><code>name</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><em><code>postMessage()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event\"><code>message</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/messageerror_event\"><code>messageerror</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><strong><code>BroadcastChannel.postMessage()</code></strong> は、任意の種類の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a> のメッセージを、同じ<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Origin\">オリジン</a>を持つ任意の<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Browsing_context\">閲覧コンテキスト</a>内の各リスナーに送信します。 メッセージは、チャネルに結び付けられた各 <code>BroadcastChannel</code> を対象とした <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/message\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">message</a></code> イベントとして送信します。</p>\n\n<p></p><div c